Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.43,0:23:37.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}吳市 上條街八百零八號
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.93,0:23:37.80,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.93,0:23:38.86,Default,,0,0,0,,那我們先走了
